     FAM#PP55 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  12 LBLID
     I                                        1   6 LTYPE
     I                                        7  12 SEQ
     I                                        7  120SEQ#
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WTIME
     I                                        7  140SDATE
     I                                        1   60STIME
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W#PGM
     I                                      244 253 W#WSID
     I                                      254 263 W#USER
     I                                      264 269 W#JBNO
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           ID     12
     C                     PARM           LBLS    4
